Package: indi-celestronaux
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI driver for Celestron mounts in AUX mode.
 .
 This is a driver for Celestron telescope mounts working in the AUX mode without hand controller.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
